Former Public Investment Corporation CEO Dan Matjila's testimony is highly anticipated due the role he played at the commission during his almost four-year tenure. JOHANNESBURG - Former PIC CEO Dan Matjila returns to the stand at the PIC Inquiry after short proceedings on Monday. Matjila had his first day at the commission to give his side of the story. His testimony is highly anticipated due the role he played at the commission during his almost four-year tenure. WATCH: Dan Matjila continues testimony at PIC Inquiry 